title: CVS Health 's number of stores 2005 to 2018
summary: Overall Number of stores has increased over the Year.
Number of stores is roughly constant from 2011 to 2014, gradually increasing from 2014 to 2015, and finally roughly constant from 2015 to 2018.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Number of stores, about 9967.0 was reported at Year 2018
The lowest Number of stores, of value 7388.0 was reported at Year 2011
